  "title": "Virginia Fair Housing Law;  regulations defining terms related to unlawful conduct.",
  "summary": "Virginia Fair Housing Law; unlawful conduct. Directs the Fair Housing Board to promulgate regulations defining \"quid pro quo harassment,\" \"hostile environment harassment,\" and other terms related to unlawful conduct under the Virginia Fair Housing Law. The bill directs the Fair Housing Board to adopt emergency regulations to implement the provisions of the bill.",
